    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-09-14T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="359"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d359">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Iglesias</persName> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San José, Costa Rica</hi>
                        </placeName>,<lb/>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 14, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The people and Government of Costa Rica are profoundly moved by the death of
                    President McKinley, and renew, therefore, expression of their sympathy to the
                    people and Government of the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rafael Iglesias.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
